# Optional: enables "Connect Spotify" so adding a track can auto-fill
# title / artist / duration / album art. The app works fully without it
# (manual entry). Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your Client ID.
#
# 1. Create a free app at https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# 2. Add these Redirect URIs to the app settings:
#      http://127.0.0.1:5173/        (local dev — Spotify requires 127.0.0.1, not "localhost")
#      https://<your-pages-url>/      (if you deploy)
# 3. Copy the app's Client ID below.
#
# Note: Spotify no longer exposes BPM / key / energy via its API for new apps,
# so those remain manual fields.
VITE_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
